HEADWORD: Shoo
<hw>Shoo</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>interj.</pos> <ety>[Cf. G.
<ets>scheuchen</ets> to scare, drive away.]</ety> <def>Begone; away; --
an expression used in frightening away animals, especially
fowls.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

